Class CalcitePrepareImpl.CalcitePreparingStmt

RelOptTable.ViewExpander

CalcitePrepareImpl
public static class CalcitePrepareImpl.CalcitePreparingStmt extends Prepare implements RelOptTable.ViewExpander
Holds state for the process of preparing a SQL statement.

Overload this class and createSqlValidator(org.apache.calcite.prepare.Prepare.CatalogReader) to provide desired SqlValidator and custom validation logic.
